TitleSelect: Concept of Time: "20 Bộ câu hỏi & Trả lời | Exploring the Concept of Time: Its Significance in Personal and Social Contexts"
ListenList: How long have you lived in this country?
Maria has lived in this country for 10 years.
John has lived here his whole life, 25 years.
Anna has been here for 5 years since she moved for work.
How long have you lived in this city/town?
Maria has been in this town for 3 years.
John has always lived in this city.
Anna moved to this city 2 years ago.
How long have you lived in your apartment/house?
Maria has lived in her apartment for 6 months.
John has been in his house for 10 years.
Anna just moved into her new house last month.
How long have you been married?
Maria has been married for 8 years.
John is not married.
Anna has been married for 3 years.
How long have you known your best friend?
Maria has known her best friend for 15 years.
John has known his best friend since high school, about 10 years.
Anna met her best friend at work 4 years ago.
How long have you studied English?
Maria has studied English for 5 years.
John has been learning English since elementary school.
Anna has studied English intensively for 2 years.
How long have you gone to this school?
Maria has attended this school for 2 years.
John has been going to this school for 4 years.
Anna is in her first year at this school.
How long have you had your car?
Maria has had her car for 3 years.
John bought his car 5 years ago.
Anna has just bought a new car 6 months ago.
How long have you had your cat?
Maria doesn't have a cat.
John has had his cat for 2 years.
Anna has had her cat since she was a kitten, 7 years.
How long have you had your dog?
Maria has had her dog for 4 years.
John doesn't have a dog.
Anna recently adopted her dog, it's been 3 months.
How long have you had your business?
Maria has run her business for 10 years.
John started his business 2 years ago.
Anna doesn't own a business.
How long have you had your house?
Maria has lived in her house for 8 years.
John has been in his house for 10 years.
Anna bought her house last year.
How long have you been awake?
Maria has been awake since 6 AM.
John woke up at 8 AM.
Anna has been awake for an hour, since 7 AM.
How long have you smoked?
Maria doesn't smoke.
John has smoked for 5 years.
Anna quit smoking 2 years ago after smoking for 10 years.
How long have you dated your partner?
Maria has dated her partner for 2 years.
John is single.
Anna has been dating her partner for 3 years.
How long have you studied?
Maria has been studying for her degree for 4 years.
John is in his second year of studying law.
Anna has studied for her exams for the past month.
How long have you traveled?
Maria traveled for 6 months last year.
John took a 2-week trip last summer.
Anna has been traveling for 3 years for work.
How long have you worked at your job?
Maria has been at her job for 7 years.
John started his job a year ago.
Anna has worked at her current job for 5 years.
How long have you known your neighbors?
Maria has known her neighbors for 3 years.
John has known his neighbors since childhood.
Anna has just met her neighbors 2 months ago.
How long have you been using social media?
Maria has been on social media for 8 years.
John started using social media 10 years ago.
Anna joined social media 5 years ago.
